    "en": {
      "title": "5 lakh vehicles received fuel.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "536,055 vehicles received fuel from last (21st) to yesterday (28th) night through National Fuel Permit and 536 fuel filling stations in QR. Electricity and Energy Minister Mr. Kanjana Wijesekara said that only yesterday 187,005 fuel was purchased according to the code.",
        "The minister added that currently 826 fuel filling stations are compliant with the National Fuel Permit System and a total of 4,479,376 vehicles have been registered as of last night."
      ],
